HEADWORD: Pooh-pooh
<hw>Pooh`-pooh"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make light
of; to treat with derision or contempt, <as>as if by saying
<ex>pooh</ex>! <ex>pooh</ex>!</as></def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>
<rj><au>Thackeray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
